            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "NISV is good. Fees are too high.\n\n\"Admission fees are equivalent to 1 month Tuition fees for new admission & at the time of getting promoted to Grades I, IX & XI.\"\n\nEven if your kid is studying in same school, then also they are charging Admission fees. I am not sure where this rule comes from.  This in not justifiable.\n\nIf from other school, then it's fine.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
